---
title: Double Pork Spaghetti Bolognese with Fresh Salad
description: You can't beat the feeling of sitting down to a hearty bowl of bolognese! In this version, the delicate mixture of tomato, cream, mirepoix and thyme will please your taste buds and warm your soul.
